*  4051 ASSEMBLER EXAMPLE PROGRAM** TO TRY THE ASSEMBLER PREFORM THE FOLLOWING OPERATIONS :**(1)FROM BASIC - PUSH "AUTO LOAD" KEY : THIS LOADS DDT DEBUGGER.*(2)AFTER DDT PROMPT APPEARS ON SCREEN TYPE "3H" : THIS FINDS MAG*                                                  TAPE FILE # 3.*(3)AFTER SYSTEM FINDS FILE # 3 TYPE "}" : THIS STARTS ASSEMBLING*                                          FROM MAG TAPE FILE.*(4)AFTER ASSEMBLY IS DONE TYPE "5000;J" : THIS JSR'S TO 5000 HEX*                                          THUS STARTING PROGRAM*                                          ASSEMBLED INTO MEMORY.*(5)TO EXIT PROGRAM EITHER HIT BREAK TWICE OR HIT "CTRL". NOTE*                                          THAT THIS PARTICULAR*                                          EXAMPLE PROGRAM IS NOT*                                          SELF TERMINATING. SOME*                                          PROGRAMS WILL HAVE A*                                          "RTS" AT THE END, THUS*                                          RETURNING TO DEBUGGER.*5000      * STARTING ADDRESS*ZBOUNCING NOP          CLR 00A8          CLR 00A9          CLR 00AA          CLR 00AB          JSR 0CBBF * INIT DISPLAY          LDX #5800 * INIT POINTER          LDAA #01 * DO A MOVE          STAA 00A5          LDAA 00,X * STARTING X          STAA 00AA * HI X          LDAA 08,X          STAA 00AB * LO X          LDAA 10,X * STARTING Y          STAA 00A8 * HI Y          LDAA 18,X          STAA 00A9 * LO Y          JSR 0CB81 * MOVE VECTORZSTART    LDX #5800 * INIT POINT POINTER          LDAA 87AA * TEST KEYBOARD CONTROL KEY          ANDA #02          BNE ZX+DELX * IF NOT ZERO THEN DO DISPLAY          RTS * ELSE BACK TO THE DEBUGGERZX+DELX   LDAA 08,X * X=X+DELTA X          LDAB 00,X          TST 30,X * TEST FOR ADD OR SUBTRACT          BEQ ZXADD * IF ZERO THEN ADD          SUBA 20,X * ELSE SUBTRACT          SBCB #00          BCC ZNOLEFT * IF NO CARRY THEN NOT LEFT WALL          CLRA * ELSE LEFT WALL          CLRB          COM 30,XZNOLEFT   STAA 08,X          STAA 00AB          STAB 00,X          STAB 00AA          JMP ZY+DELYZXADD     ADDA 20,X          ADCB #00          CMPB #03          BLE ZNORIGHT * IF <= ZERO THEN NOT RIGHT WALL          LDAA #FF * ELSE RIGHT WALL          LDAB #03          COM 30,XZNORIGHT  STAA 08,X          STAA 00AB          STAB 00,X          STAB 00AAZY+DELY   LDAA 18,X * Y=Y+DELTA Y          LDAB 10,X          TST 38,X * TEST FOR ADD OR SUBTRACT          BEQ ZYADD * IF ZERO THEN ADD          SUBA 28,X * ELSE SUBTRACT          SBCB #00          BCC ZNOBOTTOM * IF NO CARRY THEN NOT BOTTOM WALL          CLRA * ELSE BOTTOM WALL          CLRB          COM 38,XZNOBOTTOM STAA 18,X          STAA 00A9          STAB 10,X          STAB 00A8          JMP ZDRAWZYADD     ADDA 28,X          ADCB #00          CMPB #02          BLE ZNOTOP * IF <= ZERO THEN NOT TOP WALL          LDAA #FF * ELSE TOP WALL          LDAB #02          COM 38,XZNOTOP    STAA 18,X          STAA 00A9          STAB 10,X          STAB 00A8ZDRAW     CLR 00A5 * DO A DRAW          JSR 0CB81          INX          CPX #5808          BEQ ZSTART          JMP ZX+DELX**5800      * TABLE STARTING ADDRESS*"02.      * HX0"03.      * HX1"00.      * HX2"03.      * HX3"02.      * HX4"00.      * HX5"03.      * HX6"00.      * HX7"00.      * LX0"0F.      * LX1"81.      * LX2"0F.      * LX3"00.      * LX4"F1.      * LX5"7F.      * LX6"F1.      * LX7"02.      * HY0"00.      * HY1"01.      * HY2"02.      * HY3"00.      * HY4"02.      * HY5"01.      * HY6"00.      * HY7"FE.      * LY0"70.      * LY1"7F.      * LY2"8E.      * LY3"00.      * LY4"8E.      * LY5"7F.      * LY6"70.      * LY7"01.      * DELTA X0"02.      * DELTA X1"03.      * DELTA X2"04.      * DELTA X3"05.      * DELTA X4"06.      * DELTA X5"07.      * DELTA X6"08.      * DELTA X7"08.      * D